This source contains:
* resources/nona-placeholder-embedder: source written for this extension
* icon.png: package icon
* README: this file
* everything else was generated by the mozilla add-on sdk

To install the extension from source:
1. Zip up all the contents into a *.xpi file.  xpi is the same format as a
   zip file, so you should be able to zip it up and then rename it.
2. Drag-and-drop the .xpi file onto Firefox.
3. ouallah